snippet.title: Lilian -the begining of the end-
snippet.description:
You can play it at:
https://xiri.itch.io/lilian-the-beginning-of-the-end


An Angel falls in love with a boy who talks to the skies. 
Who is he talking to? 
A forbidden love story during summer time.
